citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 0945 on
24-Jan-18.
Arrived at facility and called licensee - left voicemail. Waited half an hour and called coordinator regarding
availability for inspection. Left card with phone number and time of attempted inspection at the door.
